<item>
<title>读书与不读书的人区别有哪些？</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/nhtWTJjlbJ</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/nhtWTJjlbJ</guid>
<description>&lt;p data-mpa-powered-by=&quot;yiban.io&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;“读书与不读书的人区别有哪些”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;“不读书的人搬家比较方便”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;太真实了。。。买了不少书、还租房住的人都懂，每次搬家都让人头大。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/op455Hf4TuFIFtWblWx6dOHZZk0kibqJLyYkInd0u565JQLgPcxWwJIoRQZUzVTVJoIUFic37SGjrkdfShI8fC9w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;1080&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;584.516129032258&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5398148148148149&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1080&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/w7Ejt2hiaZrxFbJUemk8ncWJs2cDUbMwjqHjQ1vcRgUmUJC39UbcWZkXVgU5JSnKpox7YZI5KHVIibcfBPnaV22g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;这些书送人吧，太可惜，毕竟都是真金白银买来的。卖二手书平台吧，看到一折的回收价又忍住了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;想不到在这个寸土寸金的城市，还得给这些书交房租。。。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;现在的纸质书价格也越来越高，豆瓣知乎上推荐的各种好书，到手后发现不适合自己，既浪费钱还占空间，这样一直恶性循环总不是办法。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

